## 1. CORE BRIEF & ORACLE

### `GET /api/v1/brief/master` · `brief/router.py → master_brief()`
2-wave ThreadPoolExecutor (3 workers/wave). 2-min TTL cache. asyncio.Lock mutex.

**Wave 1 — CORE (8 fetchers, 25s timeout):**
| Key | Fetcher | Source | JSON Shape |
|---|---|---|---|
| `macro_regime` | `fetch_macro_regime` | MacroRegimeDetector | `{ regime, inflation_score, growth_score, modifier: { long_penalty, short_penalty } }` |
| `fed_intelligence` | `fetch_fedwatch` | FedWatchEngine (yfinance ZQ futures) | `{ rate_path: { current_rate, current_range, next_meeting, days_away, terminal_bps, may_p_hike/hold/cut, regime_multiplier }, full_path: [...] }` |
| `economic_veto` | `fetch_veto` | TECalendarScraper | `{ hours_away, next_event, tier, confidence_cap, upcoming_critical: [{event, date, time, consensus, previous}] }` |
| `nowcast` | `fetch_nowcast` | ClevelandFedNowcast | `{ cpi_mom, core_cpi_mom, pce_mom, core_pce_mom, cpi_yoy, pce_yoy, updated }` |
| `dynamic_thresholds` | `fetch_thresholds` | DynamicThresholdEngine (FRED) | `{ core_pce: { HOT, COLD, consensus, std_dev }, non_farm_payrolls: {...}, cpi: {...} }` |
| `hidden_hands` | `fetch_hidden_hands` | BrainManager (politicians, insiders, Fed speakers) | `{ politician_cluster, hot_tickers, insider_net_usd, fed_tone, hawk_count, dove_count, divergence_boost, spouse_alerts, finnhub_signals, top_divergence }` |
| `derivatives` | `fetch_derivatives` | GEXCalculator (CBOE) + COTClient (CFTC) | `{ gex_regime, total_gex, spot, gamma_flip, max_pain, distance_from_max_pain, put_wall, call_wall, top_walls: [{strike, gex, signal}], cot_spec_net, cot_spec_side, cot_divergent, cot_trap }` |
| `kill_chain_state` | `fetch_kill_chain` | KillChainEngine (5-layer scan) | `{ alert_level, layers_active, narrative (200 chars), mismatches_count, regime_modifier, confidence_cap, cap_reason }` |

**Wave 2 — SIGNAL (5 fetchers, 15s timeout):**
| Key | Fetcher | Source | JSON Shape |
|---|---|---|---|
| `adp_prediction` | `fetch_adp_prediction` | ADPPredictor | `{ prediction, consensus, delta, signal, confidence, edge }` |
| `gdp_nowcast` | `fetch_gdp_nowcast` | AtlantaFedGDPNow | `{ gdp_estimate, consensus, vs_consensus, signal, edge }` |
| `jobless_claims` | `fetch_jobless_claims` | JoblessClaimsPredictor | `{ consensus, icsa_4wk_avg, delta, signal, confidence, edge }` |
| `pivots` | `fetch_pivots` | PivotCalculator + GEXCalculator | `{ ema_200, confluence_zones: [{level, count}], next_above, next_below }` |
| `squeeze_context` | `fetch_squeeze_context` | yfinance (SPY SI/short ratio) | `{ has_signal, score, short_interest_pct, days_to_cover, volume_ratio, price_change_5d, entry_price, stop_price, target_price, risk_reward_ratio }` |

**DISABLED fetchers (exist in `signals.py` but REMOVED from waves for OOM safety):**
- `fetch_pmi` (PMIPredictor), `fetch_umich_sentiment`, `fetch_umich_expectations` (MichiganMonitors), `fetch_current_account` (CurrentAccountMonitor), `fetch_squeeze_watchlist` (24 yfinance calls = OOM)

**Post-processing:** `regime_modifier`, `confidence_cap`, `cap_reason` injected into `kill_chain_state`. Alert engine runs. `scan_time` + `as_of` appended.

