## 2. SIGNALS AGGREGATOR (Critical — missed in v1)

### `GET /api/v1/signals` · `signals.py → get_signals()`
**4-source pipeline with regime gate + KC injection. 5-min cache.**

| Source | Fetcher | What It Produces |
|---|---|---|
| Layer 0 — Regime Gate | `StockgridClient.get_volatility_regime()` | `regime_tier` 1-4. Tier 4 = ALL SIGNALS SUPPRESSED. Tier 3 = no LONGs. |
| Source 1 — LiveMonitor | `fetch_monitor_signals()` | Real-time selloff/rally detections |
| Source 2 — AlertDB | `fetch_alert_db_signals()` | Options flow, DP divergence, earnings, fed alerts from `alerts_history.db` |
| Source 3 — DarkPoolTrend | `fetch_darkpool_signals()` | 5d DP position + GEX Layer 2 composite signal |
| Source 4 — MorningBrief | `fetch_morning_brief_signals()` | Pre-market verdict (fallback only when other 3 are empty) |

**Kill Chain injection (`_inject_kill_chain`):**
- Economic veto: ≤0.5h → confidence=0 BLOCKED, ≤2h → cap 35%, ≤6h → cap 50%, ≤24h → cap 55%
- BOOST → +15 confidence (cap 99), HARD_VETO → -30 (floor 20, cap 30)
- Macro regime: STAGFLATION/RECESSION → long_penalty applied to confidence

**Other signals endpoints:**
| Endpoint | Purpose |
|---|---|
| `GET /signals/master` | Only ≥75% confidence signals |
| `GET /signals/divergence` | DP confluence / options divergence from DPDivergenceChecker |
| `GET /signals/history` | Raw alerts from `alerts_history.db` |
| `GET /signals/scorecard` | P&L tracker: signal_price vs current_price, win/loss/flat |
| `GET /signals/morning-brief` | Raw morning brief data |
| `POST /signals/outcomes/check` | Check active signals against current prices |
| `GET /signals/outcomes/scorecard` | P&L scorecard from outcome tracker DB |
| `POST /signals/take-trade` | Register signal for outcome tracking |
| `GET /economic-releases` | FRED capture DB releases (last N days) |
| `POST /economic-releases/capture` | Trigger FRED capture run |

